  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/773d5ab1423b3cb1126089c456556a0c.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><i>Light of Hope 1 Fungi Spirulina</i> is a challenging strategy wargame, in which the player will play as an adventurer, from meeting to fighting alongside various partners with distinctive abilities, building the strongest adventurer team step by step!<br>Carefully designed maps and tactically variable enemies, so that every move is full of games, each enemy needs to go all out. The control of the battlefield and the formation will directly determine the life and death of the squad!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story introduction</h2>This story is about a group of people who were chosen to fight against oppression and gain freedom after the Earth was enslaved by an alien race. The storyline is light and witty, and the characters are colorful. In addition to the standard ending of the game, the game also contains a <strong>hidden true ending</strong> for you to discover.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/e87b6cf217de1965b9636e4da5bffe71.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/e87b6cf217de1965b9636e4da5bffe71.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/e87b6cf217de1965b9636e4da5bffe71.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2>Meet interesting partners with distinctive features, each with their own <strong>exclusive skills</strong> and different fighting styles, use their abilities to build your all-around team!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/53f7c923e47cbdde07479571e5eb3948.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/53f7c923e47cbdde07479571e5eb3948.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/53f7c923e47cbdde07479571e5eb3948.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The enemy has a wide variety of tactics[/b], such as fire at full strength to cause attrition, quick backward sneak attacks on priests, and side raids on both sides, so every action is a wonderful game of combat.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/69c9f77b43049966afc9198cd33f611c.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/69c9f77b43049966afc9198cd33f611c.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/69c9f77b43049966afc9198cd33f611c.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Carefully designed maps with access to <strong>favorable terrain</strong> such as woods, valleys, castles, and villages give key bonuses and a huge advantage for combat. At the same time, <strong>terrain such as cliffs and narrow passages can also limit the squad's standings</strong>, and the choice of terrain for battle will directly affect success or failure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/be642ac5417f67f74634855d35d3689e.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/be642ac5417f67f74634855d35d3689e.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/be642ac5417f67f74634855d35d3689e.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each character has <strong>exclusive battle animations</strong> and <strong>critical hit animations</strong>, and will <strong>have different battle animations</strong> depending on their abilities!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/2bbe8bc0ce7f195fc16a0c823f57bd82.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/2bbe8bc0ce7f195fc16a0c823f57bd82.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/2bbe8bc0ce7f195fc16a0c823f57bd82.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/7a6cdff38a6ac8ed518721cc8199f7c1.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/7a6cdff38a6ac8ed518721cc8199f7c1.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/7a6cdff38a6ac8ed518721cc8199f7c1.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/8f37b7531403bfb5cfebdc2f468158a1.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=320 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/8f37b7531403bfb5cfebdc2f468158a1.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/8f37b7531403bfb5cfebdc2f468158a1.mp4?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features a <strong>reins mount system</strong> that allows you to ride mounts by using reins in order to change the way units move!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/9612cc1498b9b41853933673e3b9edf2.poster.avif?t=1732003164\" width=326 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2256600/extras/9612cc1498b9b41853933673e3b9edf2.webm?t=1732003164\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>For hardcore players looking for a higher challenge, we've also got <strong>hard mode</strong> where teammates will <strong>permanently retire</strong> once they die!",
